      <title>Coinbase 的「萬物交易所」野心：當加密貨幣遇上預測市場</title>
      <link>https://bnextmedia.github.io/AINEXT/posts/20251226-coinbase-everything-exchange-prediction-markets/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Dec 2025 11:00:00 +0800</pubDate>
